actions.message:
``!buy`` to buy the script.
``!getRole`` to get buyer role, works only for previous buyers.
``!getScript`` to get the script, works only for buyers.
``!resetHwid`` resets your hwid, works only for buyers.
``!whitelist @user reason`` Whitelists the mentioned user for that reason.
``!blacklist @user reason`` Blacklists the mentioned user for that reason.
``!forceResetHwid @user`` resets the hwid of the mentioned user.
``!WhoIs`` Dms you the info of that user, encrypted HWID, Key, discord ID (johnm7 and aztup only).
``!whitelist2 reason`` Sends a whitelist of the madcity script to your dms (johnm7 and aztup only).
``!blacklist2 Paypal_Email reason`` blacklists the person with the whitelist reason (johnm7 and aztup only) .
